data.description: Home with many possibilities... This home features 1,923 of living space, 4 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, Lot size 22,500. As you enter the home you are welcomed into a Living room with Fireplace, Formal Dining Room, Kitchen with Granite countertops and a Breakfast Area, Master Bedroom and Bathroom with a walk-in closet, the other 3 bedrooms are ample sized rooms, Individual Laundry room off the kitchen, 2 Car Garage, House is on Septic, There is also a storage shed with Swamp Cooler and has electricity.
